skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the movie trivia
des: This skill will allow you to test your knowledge about Hollywood movies, awards and actors/actresses. The Movie trivia will ask you questions with 4 answers to choose from and you will have to tell the Answer number. You will be given 1 point for each correct answer.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
